# Cultureshock

}}
Cultureshock is a documentary television series on A&E. Each episode focuses on a moment that shocks American culture. The episodes are directed by different people every week.
Episodes
| ShortSummary    = Death of Michael Jackson and the reaction from his fans and the people who worked with him.
| LineColor       = #120ff0
}}
| ShortSummary    = Reality show The Osbournes and its influence on later reality shows such as Keeping Up with the Kardashians.
| LineColor       = #120ff0
}}
| ShortSummary    = Tabloid talk shows such as The Jerry Springer Show and The Phil Donahue Show and how they influenced today's YouTubers.
| LineColor       = #120ff0
}}
| ShortSummary    = The making of Freaks and Geeks and where the makers are today.
| LineColor       = #120ff0
}}
| ShortSummary    = Chris Rock remembers how he prepared for the HBO special Chris Rock: Bring the Pain.
| LineColor       = #120ff0
